<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><placeName>8 Dover St. 
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/>Piccadilly</placeName> 
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><date when="1865-05-12">12<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> May 1865</date></p>
<lb/>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Mills</p><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I am not at
<lb/>all anxious to be
<lb/>examined by the
<lb/>committee now
<lb/>sitting but rather
<lb/>than let <choice><sic><persName>Burton</persName>s</sic><corr><persName>Burton</persName>'s</corr></choice>
<lb/>assertions pass
<lb/>uncontradicted
<lb/>I would undergo

	<pb facs="liv_002701_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>the ordeal - <space extent="1" unit="chars"/>His
<lb/>assertions about
<lb/>missionaries are
<lb/>monstrous and
<lb/>false and as I
<lb/>understand he
<lb/>was allowed to
<lb/>make them why
<lb/>not take in a
<lb/>little evidence
<lb/>on the other side
<lb/>I know <placeName><country>Sierra
<lb/>Leone</country></placeName> - and <placeName><settlement type="town">Loanda</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>on the West Coast                

	<pb facs="liv_002701_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>the Interior - and
<lb/>I can compare
<lb/>the effects of
<lb/>missions - <w>settle<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>-ments</w> and the
<lb/>efforts of cruizers
<lb/>on both East
<lb/>and West Coasts -
<lb/>but if evidences
<lb/>on these points
<lb/>are not desired
<lb/>I must be <w>con<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>-tent</w> - I leave

              
	<pb facs="liv_002701_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>for <placeName><country>Scotland</country></placeName> on
<lb/>23<hi rend="sup underline">rd</hi> current -</p>
                
<!-- If there is a letter or similar with a closer with content such as salute or signed -->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>I am &amp;c<!-- Change as appropriate -->
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="words"/><persName><hi rend="small">D<hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi>
<lb/>David Livingstone</persName>


<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><add hand="#U" rend="small">&amp;c &amp;c
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="words"/>2 <gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="illegible"/>
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="words"/><gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="illegible"/></add></p>
<lb/>
<lb/>
